  "title": "BIM Modeller",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>•\tDevelop 3D BIM models using Revit/AutoCAD.</p>\n<p>•\tCreate high-quality renderings for design and presentation.</p>\n<p>•\tPrepare and coordinate Combined Services Drawings (CSD).</p>\n<p>•\tPerform clash detection and resolve issues using Navisworks.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<p>•\tDegree in Architecture, Engineering, or related field.</p>\n<p>•\tAt least 3 years of BIM related works experience.</p>\n<p>•\tProficient in Revit, AutoCAD, Lumion/Enscape.</p>\n<p>•\tFamiliar with MEP coordination and BIM standards.</p>",
